## § 2. Check Already Replied (browse_and_engage only — NOT for notifications)

🚨 False-positives on notification pages (our original comment has `/@{{handle_slug}}` link). Use tracking file dedup for notifications.

```bash
exec curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3847/api/browser/{{browser_profile}}/evaluate -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d @- <<'ENDJSON'
{"fn":"async () => { await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 3000)); const handleLinks = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('a[href*=\"/@{{handle_slug}}\"]')).filter(a => !a.href.includes('sidebar_menu')); const hasOurComment = handleLinks.length > 0 || /\\nYou\\n\\n\\d+\\s+(mins?|hours?|days?)\\s+ago/.test(document.body.innerText); return { alreadyCommented: hasOurComment, handleLinksCount: handleLinks.length }; }"}
ENDJSON
```
